{"tid":849055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人間蒸發】國際刑警組織主席孟宏偉返中國後失蹤 法警追查下落","createTime":"2018-10-05T11:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T13:20:57.000Z","uid":33799,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53df658ce66843bf58e604f8e9890a07e5538bea","tid":849055,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"法國警方近日透露，將會就國際刑警組織（Interpol）主席孟宏偉（64歲）失蹤展開調查。據報，孟宏偉中國公安部副部長，上周飛返中國期間據報失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n法新社及路透社引述警方消息指，孟宏偉與妻兒居住在法國里昂，自9月29日前赴中國時，就失去其消息，家人也無法聯絡他，也未能確定其身處位置。<br />\n<br />\n孟宏偉於2016年11月當選新一任國際刑警組織主席，主要負責國際追逃追贓工作，更成為首個當選國際刑警組織主席的中國人，任期至2020年才告屆滿。但有人權組織擔心，北京可能利用該組織追捕外逃的異見人士。<br />\n<br />\n國際刑警組織暫時未就孟宏偉失蹤一事作出回應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"fafdc1ba5064d517db3f07c890ea1743bef29976","tid":849055,"uid":33799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181005/58760901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58760901&d=dzHijIxb1BJdM2dR2xKuSeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=724d9b59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58760901&h=c7fb2ec9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181005/58760901</a>"},{"pid":"0b195730159e4d3d9c23307d2b287b65519aa3c8","tid":849055,"uid":39796,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"大陸好進步<br />\n大陸好安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d601dd0ed21f543a4a76684f61176c3e84ee9c","tid":849055,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0539f8fa6f76d7fc26639a9e077fb31aebf09a98","tid":849055,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b195730159e4d3d9c23307d2b287b65519aa3c8","tid":849055,"uid":39796,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"大陸好進步<br />\n大陸好安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177208b30ae9534583295b75aea400bbfa194a50","tid":849055,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/10/05/investigation-launched-chinese-head-interpol-goes-missing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2Finvestigation-launched-chinese-head-interpol-goes-missing%2F&d=dzHijIxb1BJdM2dR2xKuSeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=5f568fce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/10/05/investigation-launched-chinese-head-interpol-goes-missing/</a><br />\n<br />\nThe head of Interpol has been reported missing,  a French judicial official has said. <br />\n<br />\nMeng Hongwei, the Chinese head of the international police organisation Interpol, was reported missing by his wife in September. <br />\n<br />\nMeng, 64,  was last seen leaving for China from Interpol's headquarters in Lyon, southeast France, in late September, the judicial source said.<br />\n<br />\nMeng's wife, who lives in Lyon, where Interpol is based, contacted the police after not hearing from her husband after leaving for the trip.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Interpol said the whereabouts of its president is a: &quot;matter for the relevant authorities in both France and China.&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\nMeng was elected president of Interpol in November 2016. At the time, rights groups expressed concern that Beijing might try to use Meng's position at the body to go after dissidents abroad.<br />\n<br />\nBeijing has tried for many years to enlist the help of foreign countries to arrest and deport back to China citizens it accuses of crimes including corruption and terrorism.<br />\n<br />\nMeng's term is due to run until 2020.<br />\n<br />\nA vice minister of public security in China, he previously served as vice chairman of the national narcotics control commission and director of the National Counter-Terrorism Office for China. Interpol's main function is to provide a mechanism for police forces in different countries to notify each other of wanted suspects."},{"pid":"c4ce5f61193e6ef5cc3959ce15308472b74d7d27","tid":849055,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"用國際刑警身份拉班共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bb397348c32566aa1eec98c35e6ebfb09977b1","tid":849055,"uid":1552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:51:46.000Z","msg":"好快又拍片話自己好愛國，好撚自由架啦"},{"pid":"6b94cdf49000a2050f5142696117aa7a66df8aac","tid":849055,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"國際刑警組織名過於實"},{"pid":"987671c76dd39e626c45da93f8e4bf5bf01dbca5","tid":849055,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"黨大定國際刑警大"},{"pid":"bfac90f8872a982e79e08e365a15b25cf5f9289a","tid":849055,"uid":21398,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"國際刑警主席選中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後果只會同世衛一樣"},{"pid":"221543f409eaf192e708509e8fcce6336a62990d","tid":849055,"uid":71768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply